  "title": "Sales Consultant - FULL TIME / PART TIME",
  "description": "<p>An Digital Lock is looking for highly committed and motivated individuals with great passion for deliverance of high-quality service experience. The individual must be competent in engaing customers and is attentive to customer needs. He/she should have excellent communication skills and is able to provide value added product information to aid customers in their buying decision.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements You should possess at least 1 years of releavent experience in Retail industry.</p>\n<p>You must commit to retail hours (11-8pm) and is willing to work on WEEKENDS and Public Holidays.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>FULL TIME - Location : West / East</p>\n<p>PART TIME - Multiple locations / Roadshow activation</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Scope</p>\n<p>- Attend to walk in customers - Use your best knowledge to assist customer with their purchase - Handling of after sales paper work - Manage additional sales avenue (upon approval of management)</p>\n<p>Bonus + Commission Gross Salary range between $3K to $6K for F/T</p>",
