    "description": "<p>At AN Digital Lock, we believe in providing the best services / support and customer user experience to all our valued customers.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our company is honoured to be an Authorised Dealer for Samsung, Philips, Kaadas, Loghome, Solity, Igloohome, Schlage, ASUS, Dormakaba and Gatemen Digital Lock in Singapore and we strive to be the trusted and preferred provider of digital door locks and doors.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Quality and security are an integral part of every products. Each digital lock that we carry is designed with greatest efforts and care to provide our customer home with the highest level of security and convenience.&nbsp;</p>",
